body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Betty. How can I assist you today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm interested in checking the availability of a model I saw on your website.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I can certainly help with that. Could you please provide me with the model name and year?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, it's the 2023 Benzos SUV.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Great choice, Betty! Let me check the availability for the two zero two three Benzos SUV. In the meantime, could I have your contact number in case we get disconnected?

body.speaker: Customer
